Stephen Full https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephen_Full 0 Stephen Full (born November 13, 1969) is an American actor and comedian, known for his voice role and as Stan on the Disney Channel show Dog with a Blog, and acting role as Ash on I'm in the Band, which aired on Disney Channel's sister network, Disney XD.
